    {
      "timestamp": "2026-06-01T13:00:09Z",
      "bot": "server",
      "category": "message_edit",
      "action": "raw_message_edited",
      "actor": {
        "id": "1269188273201352768",
        "name": "Wave Management Bot",
        "display_name": "Wave Management Bot"
      },
      "target": null,
      "details": {
        "message_id": "1474762757256777851",
        "channel_id": "1474715327974609117",
        "channel_name": "\u26a1\u30fbpower-hour",
        "content": "# \u26a1 POWER HOUR \u2014 HOW IT WORKS\n\nA random event that rolls **every hour** \u2014 **10% chance** between 13:00\u201321:00 UTC, **5% chance** all other hours.\nWhen it fires, it lasts **exactly 1 hour** \u2014 then points are calculated and awarded.\n\n## \u26a1\u26a1 Double Power Hour\nEvery Power Hour has a **50% chance** to become a **Double Power Hour**, where all Wave Points earned are **2\u00d7**!\nWatch the announcement \u2014 the start embed will show `\u26a1\u26a1 DOUBLE POWER HOUR` if you're in luck.\n\n## \ud83c\udf0a How to Earn Wave Points\n\ud83d\udce8 **Messages** \u2014 every **10 messages** sent in either server \u2192 **+1 Wave Point**\n\ud83d\udc64 **Role Duties** \u2014 every **5 roles given** \u2192 **+1 Wave Point**\n\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f **Map Requests** \u2014 every **1 request** completed \u2192 **+1 Wave Point**\n\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f **Mod Commands** \u2014 every **2 mod commands** used \u2192 **+1 Wave Point**\n*(All values above are **doubled** during a Double Power Hour)*\n\n## \u23f0 When Are Points Awarded?\nAll points are calculated and awarded **at the end of the hour** in one go.\nYou will NOT receive them mid-event \u2014 keep grinding until time is up!\n\n## \ud83c\udfb2 How Does It Trigger?\nEvery hour at :00, the bot rolls for a chance to start.\n**Peak hours (13:00\u201321:00 UTC):** `10%` chance \u2014 **Off-peak:** `5%` chance\nIf triggered, there is then a **50% chance** it becomes a **Double Power Hour** (2\u00d7 points).\nEach hour is completely independent \u2014 missing one roll has no effect on the next.\nWatch this channel for the roll result every hour and for the \u26a1 event announcement.\n\n## \ud83d\udce1 Active Servers\nActivity is tracked across **Wave Free Dropmaps!** & **Wave Improvement Cord! | Loot Routes + Tips & Tricks** simultaneously.\nIt does not matter which server you are active in \u2014 both count equally.\n\n## \u26a0\ufe0f Penalties\nSpamming or cheating will get you disqualified instantly and possibly removed from staff.",
        "edited_at": "2026-06-01T13:00:09.829711+00:00",
        "note": "message was not in cache \u2014 pre-edit content unknown"
      },
      "guild_id": "1041450125391835186",
      "guild_name": "WAVE Drop Map Staff Hub"
